name: Bruno Bernardino
content:
I want to learn the ways of the Force and be a Jedi, like my father before me.

A tremor in the Force. The last time I felt it was in the presence of my old master.

name: Bruno Bernardino
content:
Still, she's got a lot of spirit. I don't know, what do you think?

Hokey religions and ancient weapons are no match for a good blaster at your side, kid. But with the blast shield down, I can't even see! How am I supposed to fight?

name: Bruno Bernardino
content: A sexy mistake. Yeah. Give a little credit to our public schools. Actually, that's still true. I'm sure those windmills will keep them cool.

name: Bruno Bernardino
content:
No... It's a thing; it's like a plan, but with more greatness.

I'm nobody's taxi service; I'm not gonna be there to catch you every time you feel like jumping out of a spaceship. All I've got to do is pass as an ordinary human being.

name: Bruno Bernardino
content: Sorry, checking all the water in this area; there's an escaped fish. It's art!

name: Bruno Bernardino
content: You've swallowed a planet! Heh-haa! No. No violence. I won't stand for it. Not now, not ever, do you understand me?!

content: This is the last post, the most ancient one.
